Invocation Name: n. h. radio
des:
New Horizon International is a Christian radio station founded in 2013 by Gary Zizi that broadcasts 24/7, spreading hope and inspiration through uplifting music and messages. Our mission is to reach people of all ages and backgrounds with the gospel of Jesus Christ, promoting faith, love, and peace. Tune in and experience the power of God's love and grace through our programs and presenters. Let New Horizon International radio be a source of comfort and encouragement in your daily life.
The skill content is in English, French and Haitian creole language.
